data.description: OPEN HOUSE THIS SAT AND SUN JANUARY 20TH and 21ST / 1 PM to 3 PM! Stunning home in a desirable North Central location! This immaculate 4 bedroom / 4 bath home boasts a spacious open floor plan, study, game room, granite countertops, new interior paint, and has been recently renovated with brand new flooring throughout! Additional 13x13 flex room can be a 5th bedroom, extra study or media room! Roof was installed a year ago. Downstairs primary suite with garden tub and dual vanities. Gas cooking, two dining areas as well as three living areas. Spacious and relaxing front porch and covered backyard patio. Located in The Preserve at Indian Springs Subdivision with a community pool, walking trails, tennis courts and playground. Exemplary Comal ISD schools! Easy access to 281 and 1604 and just minutes from shopping and entertainment.
